      "value": "What is Video Optimization?"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "Video optimization is the process of reducing video size and improving delivery to ensure fast loading and smooth playback on websites."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Why Video Optimization Matters"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "Videos are heavy resources that can slow down websites. Optimizing videos improves load speed, reduces buffering, and enhances user experience."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Best Video Formats"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "value": {
